== Reader of German needed. I think this article from Der Spiegel shows that the Equation Group's hard drive implant might be the NSA program IRATEMONK ==

Could someone fluent in German please read the Der Spiegel article at http://www.spiegel.de/netzwelt/web/equation-group-kaspersky-warnt-vor-manipulierter-festplatten-firmware-a-1018852.html and use it? I think that it was stating that the NSA's IRATEMONK Tailored Access Operations program that is listed at https://www.schneier.com/blog/archives/2014/01/iratemonk_nsa_e.html is similar to the Equation Group's hard drive malware. [[User:Jesse Viviano|Jesse Viviano]] ([[User talk:Jesse Viviano|talk]]) 01:28, 18 February 2015 (UTC)
:I found an F-Secure blog in English stating that they are one and the same at https://www.f-secure.com/weblog/archives/00002791.html. [[User:Jesse Viviano|Jesse Viviano]] ([[User talk:Jesse Viviano|talk]]) 02:17, 18 February 2015 (UTC)

